-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"3043f7d4aa00369580d45c7d1bb7c85b04dbab13","tid":1460882,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a8a83bc1b3c61b6925728025f48d8cf1160b82","tid":1460882,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"眼罩啦 象徵性啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:42:07.000Z","msg":"支持任何方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過豬咀真係有需要<br />\n成個地鐵都係毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbacb775426db5ffcae62cd0d9a5470b9b5eb59","tid":1460882,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ac06689cd56e98dc0f496391ea27607e151f1f","tid":1460882,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"試下上班族都一齊戴豬咀戴眼罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}